I upgraded to latest version 3.0.1

I receive the follow error on run of my site:

Cannot find namespace 'Vuex'.

```
import Vuex from 'vuex';
Vue.use(Vuex);
let store: Vuex.Store<IRootState> = createStore();
```

I see the breaking changes outlined for Typescript, but when i look in the current unit tests for this project i see a store still being setup the same way..  Am i missing something?

